-- Xstrata Says Some Workers Striking at Collinsville Coal Mine in Queensland
-- Rebecca Keenan
-- 2010-08-02T02:47:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/xstrata-says-some-workers-striking-at-collinsville-coal-mine-in-queensland.html

          
          
             Xstrata Plc. said some workers
employed by its mining contractor Thiess Pty Ltd., a unit of
Leighton Holdings Ltd., are on strike at the Collinsville coal
mine in Queensland.  
 Production is down during the strike, James Rickards, a
spokesman for Xstrata in Sydney, said by phone today. Xstrata is
keeping its customers informed, he said.  
